channel.title: Comments on: Jumpin Jelly Bean Tour

item.title: By: Russell Heimlich
item.dc:creator: Russell Heimlich
item.description: The Jelly Belly portraits were neat. We did buy a bag of Belly Flops but oddly they came from the Thailand factory and not the Californian one. Weird.
item.content:encoded: The Jelly Belly portraits were neat. We did buy a bag of Belly Flops but oddly they came from the Thailand factory and not the Californian one. Weird.

item.title: By: Steph
item.dc:creator: Steph
item.description: Been following the trip closely - I went to high school in Fairfield and lived in SF for three years! Aren't the Jelly Belly portraits the best?! Did you buy Belly Flops?
